NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: IS... IS THAT YOU, THRASH... ? @BY TRARRG, IT HAS BEEN MANY A YEAR...
GREAT UNCLE KRONG... WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU??

HUMGRUMP'S TROOPS... THEY HIT US WITH A SNEAK ATTACK! @THEY BLASTED THE MOUNTAIN TOP AND NOW THEY'RE MINING OUR METAL UP THERE... @I TRIED TO DEFEND THE VILLAGE... THE TROOPS GRABBED ME AND THREW ME DOWN HERE. @IT TOOK TWENTY OF 'EM THOUGH, LAD! OLD KRONG BUSTED MANY A HEAD... @THRASH... BOY... THEY'VE IMPRISONED THE VILLAGERS... YOUR PARENTS... @IT'S UP TO YOU NOW TO SAVE THEM!
WITH YOU BY OUR SIDE, KRONG!

NEPHEW... CAN'T YOU SEE THE CRATER OVER THERE? I HIT THE GROUND PRETTY HARD, Y'KNOW. @NOPE, THE END IS NEAR FOR ME... IT'S TIME FOR ME TO ASCEND... TO TROLLHALLA. @LISTEN TO ME. @AS A YOUNG ONE, YOU SHIED AWAY FROM THE WAY... OF THE METAL WARRIOR. @BUT... YOUR PARENTS AND I... WE ALWAYS SAW POTENTIAL IN YOU.
THRASH... TRARRG NEEDS YOU... TO HARNESS THAT POTENTIAL. @I KNOW... YOU... CAN DO IT...
GREAT UNCLE KRONG... REST IN GLORY. @WE'LL SAVE THE VILLAGE, YOU CAN BET ON IT.
